{"books":{"10":{"id":"8486","title":"Takt og Tone","description":"I Takt og Tone - Hvordan vi omgaas giver Emma Gad l\u00e6seren gode r\u00e5d til hensynsfuld opf\u00f8rsel og handlem\u00e5de i alle livets forhold. Takt og Tone blev udgivet i 1918 og er i dag at finde blandt klassikerne i dansk litteratur, b\u00e5de p\u00e5 grund af det unikke indblik i tidsperiodens normer, men ogs\u00e5 p\u00e5 grund af den almengyldighed, Gad advokerer for: \"Kun een Hovedregel for alt menneskeligt Samkvem bliver aldrig for\u00e6ldet. Det er den at handle mod sine Medmennesker ud fra et godt Hjerte.\"<br\/><br\/>\n\nTakt og Tone - Hvordan vi omgaas (in English: Etiquette - About Dealing with People) was published in 1918 and became a classic in Danish literature and cultural history. In the book, Gad gives the readers advice to etiquette in all aspects of life and how to treat other people with respect and kindness. (Summary by Anders) ","url_text_source":"http:\/\/www.weirdspace.info\/DanskeTekster\/EmmaGad\/Gad_DA.htm","language":"Danish","copyright_year":"1918","num_sections":"11","url_rss":"http:\/\/librivox.org\/rss\/8486","url_zip_file":"","url_project":"","url_librivox":"","url_other":null,"totaltime":"","totaltimesecs":0,"authors":[{"id":"10307","first_name":"Emma","last_name":"Gad","dob":"1852","dod":"1921"}],"url_iarchive":"","sections":[{"id":"301139","section_number":"0","title":"Forord","listen_url":"https:\/\/librivox.org\/uploads\/availle\/taktogtone_00_gad_128kb.mp3","language":"English","playtime":"0","file_name":null,"readers":[{"reader_id":"8564","display_name":"Anders \u00d8. Kristensen"}]},{"id":"301140","section_number":"1","title":null,"listen_url":null,"language":"English","playtime":"0","file_name":null,"readers":[{"reader_id":"8564","display_name":"Anders \u00d8. Kristensen"}]},{"id":"301141","section_number":"2","title":null,"listen_url":null,"language":"English","playtime":"0","file_name":null,"readers":[{"reader_id":"8564","display_name":"Anders \u00d